HEADWORD: Zoneless
<hw>Zone"less</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Not having a zone;
ungirded.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The reeling goddess with the <qex>zoneless</qex> waist.</q>
<rj><qau>Cowper.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>In careless folds, loose fell her <qex>zoneless</qex> vest.</q>
<rj><qau>Mason.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

